. Aedeagal shaft biramous with subbasal spine; shaft and spine about right-angled to basal part of shaft (
Figs 85, 86
). Pygofer lobe with median process curved dorsoposteriad (
Figs 83, 84
). Plate at apex dorsolaterally with finely striated concave region (
Figs 81, 83
). Sternite 
7
of female with W-shaped posterior margin (

Fig. 
88

).

